title: Kiss: Man, Medium-Dark Skin Tone, Woman, Medium-Light Skin Tone
description: A couple kissing, with the man having a medium-dark skin tone and the woman having a medium-light skin tone. This emoji expresses romantic love and closeness.

Apple's signature glossy 3D shading and smooth gradients imbue the figures with a warm, romantic glow, highlighting their affection through soft facial expressions and gentle curves. This emoji is a heartfelt symbol of romance, intimacy, and deep connection, perfect for expressing love and passion in messages on Apple devices.
